title: Old Navy Just Added New Styles to Their Clearance Section -- Save Up to 85%, Chic Finds Start at $1.47 | Nestia
text: Our writers and editors independently determine what we cover and recommend. When you buy through our links, E! may earn a commission. Learn more . Clear your schedule, put your phone to do not disturb, and head over to Old Navy . Why? They just added a ton of chic styles to their clearance section , and that means tank tops and more, as low as $1. Save up to 85% on dresses, sweaters , coats, activewear , and more -- everything you need for a winter capsule wardrobe . Plus, there are so many color and size options. I'm eyeing the $15 loafers and the $3 mock neck tank top .
